The paper proposes an analytical traffic model for unmanaged intersections that accounts for microscopic vehicle interactions. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), and Computer Engineering (cs.CE). The paper's focus on modeling traffic systems and optimizing policies also supports these categories.
